# Security Audit Checklist - Botium Toys

## Controls Assessment

Based on the scope, goals, and risk assessment report, the following controls were evaluated to determine if Botium Toys currently has them in place.

---

### Administrative/Managerial Controls

| Control | Status | Notes |
|---------|--------|-------|
| Least Privilege | ‚ùå NO | All employees currently have access to customer data |
| Disaster Recovery Plans | ‚ùå NO | No disaster recovery plans exist |
| Password Policies | ‚ùå NO | Current policies are weak and not enforced |
| Separation of Duties | ‚ùå NO | Not implemented |
| Access Control Policies | ‚ùå NO | Need to be established |
| Account Management Policies | ‚ùå NO | Requires implementation |

