## Compliance Assessment

### Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS)

| Best Practice | Status | Notes |
|---------------|--------|-------|
| Only authorized users have access to credit card information | ‚ùå NO | All employees currently have access |
| Credit card information is securely stored, processed, and transmitted | ‚ùå NO | No encryption in place |
| Data encryption procedures implemented | ‚ùå NO | Encryption needed for all touchpoints |
| Secure password management policies adopted | ‚ùå NO | Current policies insufficient |

**Compliance Status:** ‚ùå NOT COMPLIANT

